text:
Photos of North West wearing a corset have prompted outrage on social media, with shocked users wondering why Kim Kardashian and her husband Kanye let their four-year-old daughter step out in the accessory.

North can be seen in a set of photos taken earlier this week walking on the street with a corset on top of a peach-colored dress. The corset, which has a purple flower on it, wraps loosely around her chest and has laces crisscrossing in the front.

Corsets are usually worn by adult women looking to cinch their waists. Kim herself has advertised waist trainers, a type of corset, on social media, and credited them with helping shape her hourglass figure.

Shocked: Photos of North West wearing a corset have prompted outrage on social media, with users wondering why Kim Kardashian and Kanye West let their step out in the accessory

Outfit: The four-year-old can be seen in a recent set of photos walking on the street with a corset on top of a peach-colored dress. The corset has laces crisscrossing in the front

Doctors, however, have warned against waist trainers and pointed out that they could cause serious damage to internal organs.

In North's case, social media users were outraged that Kim and Kanye could let their four-year-old daughter step out of the house wearing such an adult garment.

As photos of North wearing the corset began circulating on Instagram, some users slammed the outfit in concerned comments.

'This is a mess', one person wrote next to the pictures. 'Why is this baby wearing a corset?'

Someone else worried that the outfit might attract sexual predators, while some called the accessory 'ridiculous' on a little girl.

Backlash: As photos of North wearing the corset began circulating on Instagram, some users slammed the outfit in concerned comments

Comments: Someone wondered how people could decide to dress 'babies' in corsets, while some called the accessory 'ridiculous' on a little girl

'What has the world come to,' one person wondered. 'We are starting to dress babies in corsets and satin. Watch people say its [sic] a trend.'

One Instagram user, however, tried to defend the corset by pointing out it is sewn onto the dress and thus doesn't hurt anyone.

But another person shot back: 'Kids need their innocence protected and too many pedophiles will see this and God knows what will happen !! Kids can dress cool, but not sexual OK!'

Along with the contentious corset and dress, North wore a black hat and a pair of customized sneakers bearing her name written in pink letters.

Message: The social media firestorm came as Kim was forced to clear things up after some of her social media followers claimed to see lines of cocaine on a table in one of her posts

Family: Kim also has a one-year-old son, Saint, with Kanye. The family is pictured posing together in their Easter 2017 shot, which Kim shared on social media

The social media firestorm came as Kim was forced to clear things up after some of her social media followers claimed to see lines of cocaine on a table in the background of one of her posts.

Kim shared a video on Twitter Tuesday, explaining that the white streaks spotted on a black table at a hotel she's staying are just part of the table's marble stone.

On Monday, she initially suggested the streaks might be leftover sugar from some candy her kids were eating.

'Come on. I don't play like that,' she said. 'I have kids. It's just not my lifestyle. I've never been like that.'
title: Outrage as North West steps out in a corset
